---
title: Beef & Mushroom Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice
description: This dish is an irresistible combination of courgette, tasty beef and garlicky rice, with the feel-good factor of cooking a filling
meal from scratch. The best part is the addition of aromatic ginger to make it super satisfying.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-mushroom-stir-fry-771de998.jpg
